        "timestamp": 1776170990561,
        "contentType": "reference",
        "category": "AI Design Tool",
        "annotation": "**Stitch** is Google's AI-powered UI generation tool for mobile and web. It focuses on rapid design ideation by generating interface layouts directly from prompts. Unlike traditional design systems (like Linear's approach in [0]), Stitch automates the initial creation phase rather than providing reusable components — a fundamentally different workflow that trades manual craft for speed.",
        "confidence": 1,
        "influencedBy": [
