        "category": "UI Polish",
        "annotation": "Jakub Król's catalog of micro-interactions and visual refinements — concentric border radii, optical alignment, interruptible animations, tabular numerals. These compound details distinguish polished interfaces from functional ones. Complements design system thinking by focusing on execution-level craft rather than component architecture.",
